  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK529">
<l>tamarākit taṟṟuṟantār cuṟṟa mamarāmaik </l>
<l>kāraṇa miṉṟi varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have been friends and have afterwards forsaken him, will return and join themselves (to him), when the cause of disagreement is not to be found in him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
